w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Nutcase-Vio-Mips-helmet-with-integrated-lights-review-actual-weight-2021-7-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Those micro USB rechargeable lights are in-molded into the dual density, two piece helmet shell with their patented “Exo-Skeleton” technology. The result is what Nutcase claims to be the lightest helmet featuring 360º lighting.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><p>On the outer shell of the helmet, you’ll find a higher density foam to protect against the initial impact while the softer inner layer of foam helps cushion the head on impact.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Nutcase-Vio-Mips-helmet-with-integrated-lights-review-actual-weight-2021-8.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Nutcase-Vio-Mips-helmet-with-integrated-lights-review-actual-weight-2021-8.jpg\" alt=\"Nutcase VIO helmet MIPS\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Nutcase-Vio-Mips-helmet-with-integrated-lights-review-actual-weight-2021-8.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Nutcase-Vio-Mips-helmet-with-integrated-lights-review-actual-weight-2021-8.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Nutcase-Vio-Mips-helmet-with-integrated-lights-review-actual-weight-2021-8-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Nutcase-Vio-Mips-helmet-with-integrated-lights-review-actual-weight-2021-8-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.c